{"tid":1028340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鬼父拿手電筒照女兒下體　辯稱「很溫暖」","createTime":"2019-02-19T12:05:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T15:32:19.000Z","uid":35468,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c16dd904cd2f0f2b0b9e6b391b2b24aeabca2a1a","tid":1028340,"uid":35468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T12:05:50.000Z","msg":"出版時間：2019/02/19 16:48<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190219/1520075/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190219%2F1520075%2F&d=xc0devjmTjk1MRQhR5SRZzH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=e199740d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190219%2F1520075%2F&h=ac196ebb\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190219/1520075/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190219/640_b65b8232afb67c937dacd2355bfd3aed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190219%2F640_b65b8232afb67c937dacd2355bfd3aed.jpg&h=65dde355&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新北市一名鬼父涉嫌從2012年女兒9歲大開始，多次趁女兒熟睡，撫摸女兒下體逞慾，還拿手電筒照射女兒下體「觀察」，直到前年女兒上國中，決定不再隱忍，自行到派出所報案，才揭發獸父淫行。新北地檢署根據鬼父供詞，認定他猥褻女兒2次，今依乘機猥褻罪將這名鬼父起訴，並建請法院依據《兒童及少年福利與權益保障法》加重其刑。<br />\n<br />\n起訴指出，少女和父母同住新北市，她的父親卻從2012年8月間她才9歲大開始，趁她熟睡時，進入房內偷摸她的大腿，甚至撫摸她的下體。有一次不僅直接脫掉她的褲子，還拿手電筒照射她的下體再猥褻逞慾。<br />\n<br />\n少女始終不敢聲張，直到前年間上了國中，決定不再隱忍，逕自走到派出所報案，也被警方通知社工緊急安置。少女的母親對於女兒被緊急安置感到一頭霧水，追問才知枕邊人對女兒伸狼爪。<br />\n<br />\n少女的父親坦承曾撫摸女兒下體2次，辯稱只是想要拉近和女兒的關係，覺得這樣「很溫暖」。檢方認為，少女在警詢時指控父親以每個月3、4次的頻率猥褻她，但並沒有其他證據可以佐證，因此僅依父親坦承的2次犯行定罪，今依乘機猥褻罪起訴狼父。（游仁汶／新北報導）"},{"pid":"5870c515ebee79bd1e0153cc18fbd53071fdc7f5","tid":1028340,"uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T12:07:30.000Z","msg":"用電筒會happy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d5ea63269072542b4eb2c7660163d50cebff649","tid":1028340,"uid":71393,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T12:08:54.000Z","msg":"新北市<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65b2c58859dae61fcd597899d2adf42e4cfe6430","tid":1028340,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T12:09:08.000Z","msg":"辯稱只是想要拉近和女兒的關係，覺得這樣<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「很溫暖」</span></span>"},{"pid":"898ecfaadcdc878a97e5aeeb32c36063c7c86d99","tid":1028340,"uid":27675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T12:28:17.000Z","msg":"其實係咪台灣人個個對住啲法官都會鳩噏？"},{"pid":"78311c328823747c99ea004dc3bce1f84085a364","tid":1028340,"uid":47954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T12:42:37.000Z","msg":"新北gooooaaaaalllllll<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b6835cac45dc66a51cd4b9d24bfc7c96be9672c","tid":1028340,"uid":23162,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T13:54:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">女童下體現新北精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"1a6022561761b7889b0a3777f5f3429d508c769f","tid":1028340,"uid":106375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T13:56:36.000Z","msg":"條鳩充曬血真係唔方唔溫暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7792107942fdf51a1f8bebebd3866d05c45312a6","tid":1028340,"uid":160147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T15:32:19.000Z","msg":"前世情人"}]}